{"tid":1246233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔成功投稿《金融時報》 論述港人進化抗爭模式","createTime":"2019-06-20T15:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T15:25:41.000Z","uid":51447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ff3bf0f85599c33ce305581f9c15af1668ce9e84","tid":1246233,"uid":51447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:25:41.000Z","msg":"香港「反送中」浪潮未有因特首林鄭月娥「真誠道歉」冷卻，反而越演越烈。近日大肆報道抗議消息的連登討論區宣佈，已成功在英國《金融時報》投稿，講述今次香港人進化後、沒有領袖的抗爭模式。<br />\n<br />\n文章率先今天在《金融時報》網上版刊登，明天亦會在《金融時報》報章刊出。投稿網民強調文章在《金融時報》刊出，雖然不算很大成就，亦未必值得連登仔、真正香港人開心，但已證明外國媒體仍然非常關注香港人，亦希望香港人最終成功創造歷史。<br />\n不過網上版文章刊登後不久便被抽起，投稿網民解釋由於文章最初採用筆名「連登仔」，但《金融時報》要求用回撰寫人的真實姓名，故文章暫時下架，已經盡速處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190620/59739956?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2FLeVP_I-928Uvi6rg0uWGcsQoxvITF-rxbiBBKrlQKiNI8N6RFTk319U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190620%2F59739956%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2FLeVP_I-928Uvi6rg0uWGcsQoxvITF-rxbiBBKrlQKiNI8N6RFTk319U&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rantmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=b2001840\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190620%2F59739956%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2FLeVP_I-928Uvi6rg0uWGcsQoxvITF-rxbiBBKrlQKiNI8N6RFTk319U&h=aa4ac14a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190620/59739956?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2FLeVP_I-928Uvi6rg0uWGcsQoxvITF-rxbiBBKrlQKiNI8N6RFTk319U</a>"}]}